# Project-wide ShellCheck configuration
# See: https://github.com/koalaman/shellcheck/wiki/Configuration

# Mirror Trunk's primary ShellCheck configuration so direct `shellcheck`
# invocations behave the same as `trunk check`.
enable=all
source-path=SCRIPTDIR
disable=SC2154

# SC1091: Not following sourced files — dynamic sourcing pattern is used in
# the repo, but Trunk's config does not disable this check, so we keep it
# enabled here as well for consistent behavior.
# SC2034: Unused variables — many are exported for child process consumption
# disable=SC2034
